Class FsService

  • java.lang.Object
    • Service
      • be.ppareit.swiftp.FsService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class FsService
extends Service
implements java.lang.Runnable
    FsService is the administrator service: it starts up SessionThreads, keeps the ftp server running and shuts it down.
    Author:
    David Revell, Pieter Pareit
